35	/**
36	 * A suite's identity block — datasource avatar + name + connection/env — shared
37	 * by the browse-grid card and the master list row so the two never drift. The
38	 * name renders as plain text (never an `<h4>`), so only the detail panel owns
39	 * the suite heading. `description` is opt-in (the grid card shows it; the row
40	 * doesn't).
